name: 30 MINUTES of BUSY Plane Spotting at LAX Los Angeles International Airport (4K)
description:
Los Angeles International Airport (LAX) is one of the busiest airports in the world, and is home to some truly amazing variety in terms of international airlines.

In mid-March of this year, I flew down with a couple good friends for a few days of warmth and plane spotting, and filmed these 30 minutes worth of aviation at Southern California's largest airport! Enjoy!
